            Yes, we offer volume discounts for practices and group orders. Get in touch to discuss your needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section id="contact" class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-600 to-cyan-700 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-white rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Choose the next step that matches your intent</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-cyan-100 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Choose whether you need technical documents, product-fit guidance, or a commercial response. The path should match the stage of your evaluation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/15 bg-white/10 p-8 backdrop-blur">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-cyan-100">Learn</p>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-bold">Review the clinical pack</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-cyan-50/90">Best for clinicians who want to review workflow sheets, part numbers, and support material before trial or purchase.</p>
          <a href={`${base}resources/downloads/`} class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-cyan-700 hover:bg-cyan-50">
            Download resources
